<div id="text">
<p>
This website was created to further inform people about the object they use everyday, intentionally or non-intentionally: Technology.
<br />
Often people use technology without a second thought. Many people often require technology to complete tasks throughout their everyday routine. This is because our society, as well as the world, has become reliant on technology, and there is a reason for that.
<br />
But why has our society become so reliant upon technology, and how in about 15 years has it taken over the world in a larger way than it has before?
<br />
This website will take you through the history of technology, form the creation to present day. Through this, we hope that you will learn why technology is not as simple as we think, and why it is crucial to society today.
 </p>
</div>

